    <PackageTags>bdd;tdd;testing;framework;behavior driven development;acceptance criteria</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Rewritten Core mechanisms to support multiple platforms (.NET Standard, .NET Framework), async test execution, extensibility and in-code configuration.</PackageReleaseNotes>
